artnerships noted).,MP Materials — Dec 2021: announced U.S. magnet factory and GM supply agreement. Urban Mining Company — received $28M DPA Title III funding (2020-2021). Lynas — planning US separation facility (announced/planned). Energy Fuels — began producing mixed RE carbonate from monazite (2021).
